default(
defaultand 
defaultthe
default UK also experienced the largest annual
default increase 
defaultin
default the EU)
default.
default  
defaultOLAF estimates that illicit tobacco costs the EU €10 billion a year in lost revenue,
default while HMRC estimates the UK loss at nearly £2
default 
defaultbillion.
default  
defaultThe full cost is likely to be even higher than this due to broader consequences, notably:
