default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultHowever, tobacco smugglers rarely face the maximum penalty, and Trading Standards have recommended that the Sentencing Guidelines issued to the courts be reviewed.
default  Since 2010/11 approximately 43.5% of sentences in 
defaultEngland and Wales 
defaultwere non-custodial or suspended sentences, and in Northern Ireland 
defaultthis figure
default was much higher.
default  
