default23.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultFurther inhibiting effective deterrence is the different approach to enforcement across the country.  One success story has been in Liverpool, where t
defaulthe city’s Trading Standards’ Alcohol and Tobacco Unit was set up in 2008.  Funded 
defaultuntil
default 2015 by a further injection of £400,000, it has five full time staff and 
defaultalways prosecutes for illicit tobacco seizures, even for 
defaultcases involving as few as
default 200 cigarettes.  This stance has seen a significant drop in seizures and positive test purchase operations from a peak in 2008-2009 when first formed.  However, this level of commitment is 
defaultexceptional
default.
default&#xa0;defaultSimilarities and differences in tobaccodefault smuggling defaultindefault the UK and Ireland default24.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
