default is 
defaultcaused by several factors including high profits for relatively low risk, well organised criminal networks, t
defaulthe relatively high 
defaultprice
default of tobacco (the UK and Ireland have the highest tobacco taxes in the EU), and increasing price sensitivity 
defaultamong consumers hit by
default economic 
defaulthardship
default (which has led to a wider pattern of down trading to 
defaultlegal 
defaultcheaper tobacco products).
