default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn both countries test purchasing indicates that illicit tobacco is readily available through a variety of channels, including
default market stalls, pubs, retail outlets
default 
defaultas well as door–to–door sales, private houses, and via online ads.
